== Alpha

git clone git://github.com:activefx/alpha.git
rename alpha <new_application_name>
git remote rename origin alpha
bundle install
rake development:install
git commit -a -m 'installed alpha'

mkdir <application_name>
git init
touch README
git commit -a -m 'initial commit'
# git remote add origin path/to/origin
# git push -u origin master
git remote add alpha git@github.com:activefx/alpha.git
git checkout -b alpha
git pull alpha master
git checkout master
git merge alpha
rake development:install
git commit -a -m 'installed alpha'
# git push origin master


== Features
Support for css asset compression via the YUI compressor and javascript compression via uglifier in the production environment

